{
  "stem": "1061.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were told the war was over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we really didn't know how the was finished, who-- who fought whom and how, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We just knew that the Russians-- we were on the German territory, inside of Germany, that was liberated by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we started going back to Poland, in the way as, as we walked.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we walked to a train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we were on the train for a day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we were thrown off the train because the Russians were going back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we sat on the, on the railroad stations.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then we got on another train, got bumped off again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Whatever it is, by the time we came back closer to Poland, we were warned by a Russian officer who turned out to be Jewish, he heard us in the train.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He asked us where we were going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we said that we were going back to Starachowice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, is this a big city?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we said no, it's not a big city, it's a small town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, then you cannot go back, because there are all kinds of things happening in small towns to people who are returning.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so we said, well, where else are we going?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Where else could we go?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We have to find family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, go to only to the big cities, Lodz or Warsaw, Krakow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we went to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he gave us the name of his sister, who had an apartment.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we came, there were wall to wall people, because she was taking in everybody.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the next day, we went and found out that there's a Jewish agency that registers people, returning people, whoever, Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because there was a Red Cross that was also registering people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the Jewish agency set up their own.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we signed our name and went there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Of course, they gave us, then, rations-- food rations.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were-- we were in the agency every day, to look through the register, you see.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And sure enough, we found Uncle Alexander, who was my father's brother from Radom.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we established a household.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "First we lived-- before we found uncle, we lived in a hovel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was no electricity and nothing, just four walls that were bombed out or whatever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when Uncle Alexander came on the scene, so to say, he helped us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He went back to his hometown.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He had real property, real estate and-- he was able to get some of the money that he hid.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so when he came back, we got a very decent kind of an apartment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the three of us lived with Uncle Alexander in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And by then it was summer, summer 1945.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And subsequently, my two sisters found work in Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I went to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I was tested and admitted to the second year of high school, and I wasn't even-- before the war I didn't even finish-- I did elementary school.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But I had all this-- I knew chemistry, and I-- I mean, really.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And after all the horrible experiences that I was able to even pass a test.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But we stayed in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And my sister Krys met her present husband, Miles Lerman.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They got married in December of the same year in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And very soon--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
